				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$ \mathrm{i}.\mathrm{e}.,{S}_M=\frac{\sum_{i\in M}{s}_i}{\sqrt{\mid M\mid }} $$\end{document}i.e.,SM=∑i∈Msi∣M∣) while satisfying the connectivity conditions for both protein interaction and co-expression networks.
